            <p>
               <seg rend="right">
                  <add style="textOrientation: straight" resp="other">
                     <date when="1859">1859</date>
                     <lb/>
                     <placeName ref="K00501">Batavia</placeName>
                     <lb/>
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01005">Morgan Melbourn &amp; Co.</orgName>
                     <lb/> R <hi rend="underline" n="1">
                        <date when="1859-11-06">6 Novbr</date>
                     </hi>
                     <lb/> A <date when="1859-11-10">10 Nov.</date>
                  </add>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
         <pb facs="1859_09_05_Kniffler_Dejima_von_Morgan_Melbourn_Co_Batavia_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <div>
            <p> p"<name type="ship" ref="K01513">A. R. Falck</name>."<lb/>
               <seg rend="right">
                  <placeName ref="K00501">Batavia</placeName>, <date when="1859-09-05">September 5th
                     1859</date>
               </seg>
               <lb/>
               <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">Messrs. Kniffler &amp; Co.</orgName>,<lb/>
               <placeName ref="K00507">Desima</placeName>
               <lb/>
               <placeName ref="K00502">Japan</placeName>
               <lb/> Dear Sirs,<lb/> Enclosed we have the pleasure to hand<lb/> you Invoice of
                  <measure type="volume" quantity="33" unit="kisten">33 Cases</measure>
               <term type="goods" ref="K01514">Semen Cynae</term> shipped p <name type="ship" ref="K01513">A.<lb/> R. Falk</name>" to your address amounting to <measure type="currency" quantity="2282.50" unit="gulden">
                  <term type="measure" ref="K01512">f</term>
                  <hi rend="underline">2282:50</hi>
               </measure>
               <lb/> which we trust will meat a ready sale at good prices,<lb/> we will advise you
               on another occasion in what shape<lb/> we wish the nett proceeds permitted. The <term type="logistic" ref="K01515">Bill of la-<lb/> ding</term> for this <term type="goods" ref="K01514"> medicine</term> will be forwarded to you by<lb/>
               Messrs. <orgName type="firm" ref="K01001"> Pandel + Stiehaus</orgName>. <seg rend="center">We ramain, Dear Sirs,<lb/> yours very truly, <orgName type="firm" ref="K01005"> Morgan, <hi rend="underline">Melbourn &amp; Co.</hi>
                  </orgName>
               </seg>
               <pb facs="1859_09_05_Kniffler_Dejima_von_Morgan_Melbourn_Co_Batavia_3.tif" n="3"/>
